jsonld.description:
A refined dress shirt with a fluid, architectural silhouette that reads tailored yet relaxed. Featuring long sleeves and a hidden side panel that creates a subtle cocoon shape through the back. Finished with a concealed front placket, a classic slightly exaggerated collar, and button cuffs. Cut from a soft sand washed cotton that has a gentle crinkle and comfortable breathability.
 
fit
Dane is 6'0" and typically wears a Large in tops. He's wearing the size Large here for a relaxed fit.

jsonld.description:
The Aster Dress combines lightweight pure cotton voile with exquisite lace detailing for a refined, breathable garment. Its flared silhouette and graceful hem flounce evoke effortless elegance, while wide volume sleeves and a shirt cuff with side buttons add sophisticated style. Featuring a chic round neckline with a subtle stand-up collar and button motif, this dress includes a removable matching slip for versatility. Perfect for warm days and elegant evenings, the Aster Dress embodies modern femininity inspired by the charm of Riviera gardens.
Style: 2515231023600
